  <div class="container d-flex flex-column justify-content-around text-center px-2 " id="sales-pitch">
    <h3>We strive to be a market leader with a quality and reliable PAT Testing service in Aberdeen</h3>
    <p>We are a small local business operating all over Aberdeen & Aberdeenshire. Whether you are a business owner, sole trader or landlord, we are here to help you any way we can. We use the latest in battery-powered machines, ensuring no damage to any potentially sensitive items, testing a wide range of either 110v or 240v equipment.</p>
  </div>
