            <i class="fas fa-tools fa-5x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col-8 d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pt-3">
            <h5>Internal Examination</h5>
            <p>Every single plug (non-moulded) we test undergoes an internal inspection.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-11 col-md-6 col-xl-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="row feature-card-wrapper">
          <div class="col-4 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
            <i class="fas fa-check-double fa-5x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col-8 d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pt-3">
            <h5>Double Checking</h5>
            <p>To ensure safety of your electrical equipment, both visual examination and testing are essential to identify any defects.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-11 col-md-6 col-xl-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
