          </div>
          <div class="col-8 d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pt-3">
            <h5>No Rush</h5>
            <p>A quality PAT Testing job takes time and no corners should be cut.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-11 col-md-6 col-xl-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
        <div class="row feature-card-wrapper">
          <div class="col-4 d-flex flex-column justify-content-center">
            <i class="fas fa-user-shield fa-5x"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="col-8 d-flex flex-column justify-content-start pt-3">
            <h5>Protecting Lives</h5>
            <p>Ultimately this is about protecting staff from harm and businesses from liability. For peace of mind, our fees include all the time necessary to carry out thorough examinations.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
